-- 
Petrobras Reports Fire at Texas Refinery Near Houston

-- B y   A a r o n   C l a r k
-- 
2011-12-11T12:51:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-11/petrobras-reports-fire-at-texas-refinery-near-houston-1-.html
Petroleo Brasileiro SA (PETR4)  reported a
fire at its Pasadena refinery near Houston, according to a
message left on a recorded hotline.  There were two explosions at the plant late yesterday,
according to a report on KTRK-TV Houston’s website, citing
unidentified investigators. The fire occurred in the plant’s
coker unit, it said.  The refinery has a capacity of 106,500 barrels a day,
according to data compiled by Bloomberg. The plant has coking
capacity of 12,500 barrels a day.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Aaron Clark in New York at 
 aclark27@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mike Harrison at 
 mharrison5@bloomberg.net  